item.title: By: Julian Robichaux
item.dc:creator: Julian Robichaux
item.description: <p>Well, sometimes you just gotta use what works... Web services aren't too hard until they don't work -- then they can get pretty hairy.<br /><br />Think of it this way though: you get to play with new/different stuff!<br /></p>
item.content:encoded:
Well, sometimes you just gotta use what works… Web services aren’t too hard until they don’t work — then they can get pretty hairy.

Think of it this way though: you get to play with new/different stuff!
